Traditional Moravian lentil soup

0. Soak brown lentils overnight
1. Stir onion on oil, add some flour, water and milk alternative to create roux
2. Cook lentils until they are soft
3. Mix the roux and the lentils, add mashed garlic, salt, pepper, and marjoram
4. Cook the soup some more with cut carrots or add little pieces of soy wienerwurst
